---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<div class="portal-container">
		<!-- Section 1: Identity -->
		<section class="hero-section fade-in-up">
			<div class="meaning-block">
				<p class="meaning-intro zen-mincho">意味・構造・表現の循環</p>
				<h1 class="portal-title zen-mincho">Aeternum</h1>
				<p class="meaning-description">
					文化を資産へ、感性を構造へ。<br>
					私たちは「意味」を掘り起こし、持続可能な「表現」へと昇華させるデジタルデバイスです。
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Section 2: Pillars -->
		<section class="pillars-grid">
			<!-- Shushuan (EC) -->
			<a href="/catalog" class="pillar-card fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
				<div class="pillar-bg brand-bg"></div>
				<div class="pillar-content">
					<span class="pillar-label">Sensory EC</span>
					<h2 class="zen-mincho">蒐集庵</h2>
					<p>5感を繋ぎ、物語を収蔵する、現代のアーカイブショップ。</p>
					<span class="pillar-cta">所望する →</span>
				</div>
			</a>

			<!-- Nexus (B2B) -->
			<a href="/nexus" class="pillar-card fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;">
				<div class="pillar-bg nexus-bg"></div>
				<div class="pillar-content">
					<span class="pillar-label">B2B Strategy</span>
					<h2 class="zen-mincho">NEXUS</h2>
					<p>文化監督による経営サポート。暗黙知を構造化し、ブランドの背骨を作る。</p>
					<span class="pillar-cta">共鳴する →</span>
				</div>
			</a>

			<!-- Journal -->
			<a href="/journal" class="pillar-card fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.6s;">
				<div class="pillar-bg journal-bg"></div>
				<div class="pillar-content">
					<span class="pillar-label">Cultural Insight</span>
					<h2 class="zen-mincho">Journal</h2>
					<p>日々の思索、文化の断片、構造への問い。Aeternum の筆致を綴る。</p>
					<span class="pillar-cta">覧る →</span>
				</div>
			</a>
		</section>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.portal-container {
		max-width: 1200px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
	}

	.hero-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 8rem;
		padding: 4rem 0;
	}

	.meaning-intro {
		color: var(--accent-primary);
		letter-spacing: 0.5em;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.portal-title {
		font-size: 5rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.meaning-description {
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		line-height: 2;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.pillars-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
	}

	.pillar-card {
		position: relative;
		height: 500px;
		display: flex;
		align-items: flex-end;
		text-decoration: none;
		overflow: hidden;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
		transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.165, 0.84, 0.44, 1);
	}

	.pillar-bg {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		z-index: 1;
		transition: transform 0.8s;
		opacity: 0.15;
	}

	.brand-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-primary), transparent); }
	.nexus-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50, transparent); }
	.journal-bg { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7f8c8d, transparent); }

	.pillar-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		padding: 3rem;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.pillar-label {
		display: block;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.2rem;
		color: var(--accent-primary);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.pillar-card h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-primary);
	}

	.pillar-card p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: var(--text-muted);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	.pillar-cta {
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1rem;
		color: var(--accent-primary);
		opacity: 0;
		transform: translateX(-10px);
		transition: all 0.3s;
	}

	.pillar-card:hover {
		border-color: var(--accent-primary);
		background: rgba(46, 54, 48, 0.2);
	}

	.pillar-card:hover .pillar-bg {
		transform: scale(1.1);
		opacity: 0.3;
	}

	.pillar-card:hover .pillar-cta {
		opacity: 1;
		transform: translateX(0);
	}

	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.pillars-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		.portal-title {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
		.pillar-card {
			height: 400px;
		}
	}
</style>
